<div class="heading resPageHeading">


























<h1 >How to level-up education with video games research</h1></div>

<div class="content stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resImageText section">


























		<div class="row" id="f15e123e-d7c4-40f6-98ee-41d3c87f815c">
			<div class="col-xs-12">
				<div class="thumbnail customStyle1">
					
<img src="/content/dam/research/images/newsletter/2020-07/video-games-education-0.jpg" alt="A group of university students working together at a computer"/>




					 
						<div class="caption richtextContent empty">
	
</div>
						    
					
